00:55:57.490 --> 00:55:59.870
we can just do measurement
of one quadrature component

00:55:59.870 --> 00:56:01.100
or the other.

00:56:01.100 --> 00:56:04.390
So what I hope for those of
you who haven't heard about it,

00:56:04.390 --> 00:56:06.990
what you take away
from that is that these

00:56:06.990 --> 00:56:10.150
are extremely simple elements.

00:56:10.150 --> 00:56:12.820
But by combining
